<p>Thank you for your registration at <%=@current_school.school_name%>.</p>
<p>Your application shall be sent for approval once you click the following link:
  <br/><a href="http://<%= @current_school.subdomain %>.<%= Schoolapp.config(:app_domain) %><%= url(:registration_last, :id => @parent.password_reset_key) %>">http://<%= @current_school.subdomain %>.<%= Schoolapp.config(:app_domain) %><%= url(:registration_last, :id => @parent.password_reset_key) %> </a></p>

